/*************************************************** Gerph *********
 Function:     gcontext_initdrawfilememory_scaled
 Description:  Initialise a transformed memory-backed DrawFile context
 Parameters:   memory = destination memory, or NULL to size only
               memorysize = size of destination memory
               xscale,yscale = positive DrawFile units per OS unit
               xtranslation,ytranslation = DrawFile coordinate offsets
